t should go from -1 to 2

(t<1) ? 
1 0 0 -t
0 1 0 -t
0 0 1 -t
0 0 0 1
:
(t<1+pi/2) ?
1 0 0 -1
0 cos(t-1) -sin(t-1) -cos(t-1)+sin(t-1)
0 sin(t-1) cos(t-1) -cos(t-1)-sin(t-1)

:
1 0 0 -1+t-1-pi/2
0 0 -1 1+t-1-pi/2
0 1 0 -1+t-1-pi/2


=>

1                           0                           0                   (t<1)?-t:(t<1+pi/2)?-1:-2+t-pi/2
0      (t<1)?1:(t<1+pi/2)?cos(t-1):0    (t<1)?0:(t<1+pi/2)?-sin(t-1):-1     (t<1)?-t:(t<1+pi/2)?-cos(t-1)+sin(t-1):t-pi/2
